title: "Intelligence Is Not the Bottleneck: Validating an LLM First-Pass Manuscript Score Against Peer-Review Outcomes — analysis code and data"
abstract: >-
  Reproducible analysis code, pre-registration, de-identified scored data, and LaTeX
  manuscript for a pre-registered study validating an automated LLM manuscript-scoring
  system (AIPR) against the public peer-review outcomes of ICLR 2026 on OpenReview.
